QuestData.Title: Return to Mistfall
QuestData.Description:
We have done all we can here. We know how much the mogu are a clear threat.
The forge is in great danger of falling into their hands if we lose our hold on the Vale.
Let us return to Mistfall and report to the Rajani. They will want to know what we are up against.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Stormspeaker Qian in the Silent Sanctuary in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Return to Stormspeaker Qian in the Silent Sanctuary in the Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
